title: [Quit Stallin', The Shell Game]
description: Low to the ground fixtures are placed throughout the space, nestled within some shredded cypress mulch bedding.  A claw-footed carved oak hay rack rests upon the corner floorboards, beside a porcelain produce pail.  A display table resting in the fragrant mulch shows off the appearance of a hammered steel watering trough.  Prominently nailed near the entrance is a large parchment notice.
